>> Nobody benefits
from poor health care.

00:00:12.840 --> 00:00:16.379 align:middle line:84%
Nobody benefits from
adverse reactions

00:00:16.379 --> 00:00:17.940 align:middle line:90%
to drugs and medicines.

00:00:17.940 --> 00:00:20.220 align:middle line:84%
