and reviewing from time

00:00:28.230 --> 00:00:29.610 align:middle line:90%
to time.

00:00:29.610 --> 00:00:34.260 align:middle line:84%
We do need to use surgery and
chemotherapy and radiotherapy

00:00:34.260 --> 00:00:36.300 align:middle line:90%
and drugs.

00:00:36.300 --> 00:00:40.770 align:middle line:84%
But we, I think, from the
evidence that's available,

00:00:40.770 --> 00:00:43.595 align:middle line:84%
use it too soon
and too frequently.

00:00:43.595 --> 00:00:44.970 align:middle line:84%
There are many
things that we can

00:00:44.970 --> 00:00:47.670 align:middle line:84%
do for many patients
and individuals

00:00:47.670 --> 00:00:51.060 align:middle line:84%
